de.ityx.mediatrix.api.interfaces.businessrules.client

Interface IClientObjectsControl


  • public interface IClientObjectsControl
    Contains store, delete and load functions for main objects like customers, cases, questions ... The objects can be manipulated directly before they are sent to the application server.
    was:
    ClientObjectsControl.java
